# Liabilities Insurance Policy Reinsured Excluding Current Bonus Amount

## identifier
de4600

## type
float

## definition
Report the total gross policy liability ceded under reinsurance as per prudential standards, excluding current year bonuses. Note that this differs to the accounting standards treatment.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Liabilities.Insurance.PolicyReinsuredExcludingCurrentBonus.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.04
- period=instant
